  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll get a buffet with loads of fresh options, from fruit, to pastries and freshly baked bread. The resort has a farm-to-table policy, so you'll only be getting the best quality, natural produce. Most of their ingredients are grown on the resort grounds or on local farms. We love their passion for sustainability!</p>
<p>Half board is taken in the main restaurant. The restaurant is very spacious and has a stunning outdoor terrace with a view of the sea. They serve a typical Sicilian gourmet dinner every night and because they use only the freshest ingredients, you'll be getting a true taste of Sicily. It also means they do fantastic vegan and vegetarian dishes.</p>
<p>There are two hotel bars which are great places to grab a drink and put your feet up before dinner. The Lido bar is on the beach, so you can drink cocktails on the beach whenever you like!</p>]]></cateringDescription>
