  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 55m² and they can sleep two people, plus a child aged 0 - 17 years. The rooms are bright and spacious with views out to sea through the large glazed windows that open up onto the terrace. They're decorated in a modern, comfortable style, with a focus on using natural and sustainable materials that blend with the surrounding environment. Facilities include a 12m² terrace, air conditioning, TV, Wi-Fi, minibar, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, rain shower and a hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Family Suites </strong>are about 75m² and sleep up to four people, plus a child aged 0 - 3 years. These suites have two bedrooms and two bathrooms. They're available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Double Room for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
